{"title":"login逻辑","date":"2021-12-11T14:10:26.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Dec 11, 2021","L":"12/11/2021","MM-DD":"12-11"},"link":"2021/12/11/login逻辑","tags":["javascript","登录逻辑"],"categories":["前端"],"updated":"2021-12-11T14:10:53.364Z","content":"<h2 id=\"登录逻辑\">登录逻辑<a title=\"#登录逻辑\" href=\"#登录逻辑\"></a></h2>\n<p>login.js</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br><span class=\"line\">79</span><br><span class=\"line\">80</span><br><span class=\"line\">81</span><br><span class=\"line\">82</span><br><span class=\"line\">83</span><br><span class=\"line\">84</span><br><span class=\"line\">85</span><br><span class=\"line\">86</span><br><span class=\"line\">87</span><br><span class=\"line\">88</span><br><span class=\"line\">89</span><br><span class=\"line\">90</span><br><span class=\"line\">91</span><br><span class=\"line\">92</span><br><span class=\"line\">93</span><br><span class=\"line\">94</span><br><span class=\"line\">95</span><br><span class=\"line\">96</span><br><span class=\"line\">97</span><br><span class=\"line\">98</span><br><span class=\"line\">99</span><br><span class=\"line\">100</span><br><span class=\"line\">101</span><br><span class=\"line\">102</span><br><span class=\"line\">103</span><br><span class=\"line\">104</span><br><span class=\"line\">105</span><br><span class=\"line\">106</span><br><span class=\"line\">107</span><br><span class=\"line\">108</span><br><span class=\"line\">109</span><br><span class=\"line\">110</span><br><span class=\"line\">111</span><br><span class=\"line\">112</span><br><span class=\"line\">113</span><br><span class=\"line\">114</span><br><span class=\"line\">115</span><br><span class=\"line\">116</span><br><span class=\"line\">117</span><br><span class=\"line\">118</span><br><span class=\"line\">119</span><br><span class=\"line\">120</span><br><span class=\"line\">121</span><br><span class=\"line\">122</span><br><span class=\"line\">123</span><br><span class=\"line\">124</span><br><span class=\"line\">125</span><br><span class=\"line\">126</span><br><span class=\"line\">127</span><br><span class=\"line\">128</span><br><span class=\"line\">129</span><br><span class=\"line\">130</span><br><span class=\"line\">131</span><br><span class=\"line\">132</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 定义变量判断是否是手机银行环境</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> isBank = <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 路由登录拦截 checkLogin</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 在router.js 里面的 beforeEnter: CheckLogin 的逻辑</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 排除几个只需要静默登录，不在乎成功失败的页面（即：不会跳转登录的页面）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> noToLoginPages = [<span class=\"string\">&#x27;/home&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;/order&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;/detail&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> CheckLogin = <span class=\"keyword\">async</span> (to, <span class=\"keyword\">from</span>, next) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;CheckLogin&#x27;</span>, to, <span class=\"keyword\">from</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">try</span> &#123; <span class=\"comment\">// 做一个约定，只有信任登录成功才会走到这，直接进入下一个页面，否则一切都走到 catch 里面，做登录失败的处理</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> res = <span class=\"keyword\">await</span> CifCheckLogin(to.query) <span class=\"comment\">// 信任登录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (res === <span class=\"string\">&#x27;next&#x27;</span>) next()</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">catch</span> (err) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 这里需要先排除那些只信任登录，不在乎成功失败的页面</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;信任登录失败原因：&#x27;</span>, err) <span class=\"comment\">// 这里是reject的值---没有信任登录成功的处理</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (noToLoginPages.includes(to.path)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            next()</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 除此之外,如果是接口错误，返回首页，如果是状态不对，跳转登录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            err === <span class=\"string\">&#x27;toLogin&#x27;</span> ? toLogin(to, <span class=\"keyword\">from</span>, next) : next(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;/&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/**</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * 信任登录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">CifCheckLogin</span>(<span class=\"params\">query</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;CifCheckLogin----query&#x27;</span>, query)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">Promise</span>(<span class=\"function\">(<span class=\"params\">resolve, reject</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 如果登录过，并且是成功状态，直接进入下一页</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (sessionStorage.getItem(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;webloginCode&#x27;</span>) == <span class=\"number\">1</span>) resolve(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;next&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 如果有过主动退出，应该直接跳转登录页面</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (sessionStorage.getItem(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;logOut&#x27;</span>)) reject(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;toLogin&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 如果在手机银行环境中</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (isBank) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 判断地址栏参数，如果存在 mac 即需要 TRUST 登录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (query &amp;&amp; query.mac) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">// 这里需要请求 webLogin 接口</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                webloginApi(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;TRUST&#x27;</span>, to.query, resolve, reject)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">// 如果没有参数，调手机银行插件信任登录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"built_in\">window</span>.Plugin.xxx(<span class=\"function\">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"comment\">// 这里需要对参数进行加密</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"built_in\">this</span>.utils.sm2(query).then(<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"params\">smData</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        webloginApi(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;CIF&#x27;</span>, smData, resolve, reject)</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 如果是非手机银行环境，判断地址栏是否有 token，再去请求 webLogin 接口</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (query &amp;&amp; query.token) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                webloginApi(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;UNIFINED&#x27;</span>, to.query, resolve, reject)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 调用weblogin接口</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> webloginApi = <span class=\"keyword\">async</span> (loginType, data, resolve, reject) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;webloginApi--Data: &#x27;</span>, &#123; loginType, ...data &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> res = <span class=\"keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"built_in\">this</span>.$api.user.weblogin(&#123; loginType, ...data &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        handleLoginData(res, resolve, reject)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">catch</span> (err) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        reject(err)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 处理 weblogin 接口返回值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> handleLoginData = <span class=\"function\">(<span class=\"params\">res, resolve, reject</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;returnLoginData:&#x27;</span>, res)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    sessionStorage.setItem(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;webloginCode&#x27;</span>, res.returnCode)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (res.returnCode === <span class=\"number\">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 成功</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        successData(res.uto || res)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        resolve(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;next&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 除了 1 以外的所有情况都属于失败</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        ErrorData(res, reject)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> successData = <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"params\">data</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 处理成功登录的一系列操作</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 存储 token ，user ，啥啥啥的。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 登录成功需要清除主动退出标识 logOut</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> ErrorData = <span class=\"function\">(<span class=\"params\">data, reject</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 判断状态码； 不同的状态码对应不同的情况，有些需要弹窗，有些需要啥啥的</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 不管哪样，这些都属于失败，那么就需要把 存在的一切登录信息清除掉</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 如果是账号被顶，需要主动添加 主动退出标识 logOut</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    clearLoginData()</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">switch</span> (data.returnCode) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"number\">2</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 啥啥啥</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">case</span> -<span class=\"number\">1</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 啥啥啥</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            reject(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;toLogin&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">case</span> xx:</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 啥啥啥</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 清除登录信息</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> clearLoginData = <span class=\"function\">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// localStorage.removeItem(&#x27;user&#x27;, &#x27;token&#x27;, ...)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// ...clear</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 还需要 清除一下 手机银行的登录信息</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 调手机银行登出插件做一个登出操作--控制台好像容易报错，需要对这个插件做一个容错处理</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 跳转登录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 这里需要有两种情况， 登录成功之后的返回</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 1. 路由跳转的登录    2. 接口触发的登录跳转</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> toLogin = <span class=\"function\">(<span class=\"params\">to, <span class=\"keyword\">from</span>, next</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;toLogin----&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;to:&#x27;</span>, to, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;from:&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">from</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 接口触发的话，to 和 from，相同就行，成功，失败，返回后退，都是在当前页面</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (isBank) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 插件登录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 成功之后</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 如果是路由触发</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        next() <span class=\"comment\">// 成功</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        next(<span class=\"keyword\">from</span>) <span class=\"comment\">// 失败,或者返回</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 需要考虑，插件登录，成功之后会不会刷新页面</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 刷新页面或不刷新怎么去处理</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 统一用户登录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","next":{"title":"JavaScript异步编程","link":"2021/12/02/JavaScript异步编程"},"plink":"https://rdhuang.gitee.io/2021/12/11/login逻辑/","toc":[{"id":"登录逻辑","title":"登录逻辑","index":"1"}],"copyright":{"author":"Humphrey","link":"<a href=\"https://rdhuang.gitee.io/2021/12/11/login逻辑/\" title=\"login逻辑\">https://rdhuang.gitee.io/2021/12/11/login逻辑/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}